data.description: **SELLER TO PAY CLOSING COSTS UP TO 7500$*** Move in ready. Basement rancher with two car garage, large fenced in yard with concrete pad, & deck facing the wooded view. Home backs up to the greenbelt. All new life proof vinyl flooring throughout, new light fixtures, interior doors, & remodeled main floor bathrooms. Kitchen features breakfast bar & new stainless-steel appliances. Main bedroom boasts a sky light, large bathroom with a walk-in shower, & jacuzzi tub. Lots of natural light in this home with two additional sky lights in the living room. Lower level has 4th bedroom, additional bathroom, a recreational room, & walk out access to the patio. Don't miss out on this one!
